column2: SELECT u.up_CID as CID, x.objID,   s.BestObjID, s.ra, s.dec,   dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,  s.specObjID, s.z, s.zWarning, s.class, s.subClass FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN PhotoObj p ON p.objID = x.objID  JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID ORDER by x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
